## 📖 Overview

This project explores what a personalized, AI-native listening experience feels like — recommendations that adapt to taste, lyrics that stay in sync, and playback that never stutters between tracks, whether you're on the web app or the Flutter mobile client.

## ✨ Key Features

- 🤖 **AI-powered music discovery** — recommendations driven by listening patterns rather than static genre tags
- 🎤 **Synchronized lyrics** that scroll in time with playback
- 🎨 **Dynamic UI personalization** — the interface adapts visually based on the currently playing track
- 🔊 **High-performance audio engine** built on the Web Audio API for **gapless playback** — no dead air between songs
- 📱 Shared playback experience across the Next.js web app and Flutter mobile client

