## 🚀 Getting Started

```bash
git clone https://github.com/hackerstudent29/Zenify.git
cd Zenify

# Backend
cd server
npm install
npx prisma migrate dev
npm run dev

# Web frontend
cd ../web
npm install
npm run dev

# Mobile
cd ../mobile
flutter pub get
flutter run
```

